


# <Type>(<file/func/arg>): <Task Name>
# What you cared and how you've changed.
#
# [Rule]
# 1. Task Name begins with the capital letter.
# 2. First line must be less than 50 characters.
# 3. First line must not use period at end of line.
# 4. Never blank body.
#
# [Message]
# Positive
#   Add {*A to *B}
#     - Add a feature
#     - Add test for bug #1234
#     - Add function method
#     - Add null check
#   Update {*A to *B}
#     - Update package to v1.2.4
#   Implement(Impl):実装
#     - Implement `Class::version` for filename
#   Improve:改良 (performance)
#     - Improve tests for components
#   Extend :機能拡張
#   Enhance:機能向上
#   Optimize
#   Ensure (*A is ~ed)
#     - Ensure fetch polyfill is loaded in server
#   Use {*A insted of *B}
#   Make {*A *B}
#   Sorting {*A by *B}
#     - Sorting data by id
#   Simplify {*A}
#     - Simplify Object#method code
#   Define {*A}
#     - Define `Object#method`
#   Fix/Revise(bug)  *A(filename/typo/error hundling)
#     - Fix typo in docs
#     - Fix for #1234
#     - Fix link to the spec
#   Modify(not bug)
#     - Modify an existing feature
#   Refactor {*A (a bit) (to *B)}
#   Tweak
#   Bump {*A to *B}
#     - Bump version to 2.0.0
#     - Bump the patch version to 2.0.0
#
# Negative
#   Delete {*A form *B}
#   Remove {*A from *B}/{use of *A}/{to avoid *A}
#     - Remove a feature
#     - Remove unused code
#     - Remove debug from tests
#     - Remove use of deprecated method
#     - Remove methods to avoid warnings
#   Avoid {*A to *B}
#     - Avoid method call to compact
#   Clean {up *A}/{*A up}
#     - Clean the func up
#
# Replace
#   Change {*A to *B}
#     - Change variable name
#   Move {*A from *B to *C}
#   Replace {*A with *B}
#   Rename {*A to *B}
#     - Rename `a.js` to `b.js`
#
# Git
#   Merge {*A}
#     - Merge #1234
#   Revert    to *A(commit hash)
#     @ Revert to 88a69caec37031687c7192f8a512ea
#
# Other
#   InitialCommit
#
# more sample:
# https://qiita.com/gogotanaka/items/b65e1b081fa976e5d754
# https://android.benigumo.com/20161121/git-commit-message-title/
# https://yutakatay.gitbook.io/katapedia/doc/komittomessjideyokuu
